parameters:
Mayor Orca: Gah... ohhh...!? Even after further training
since my pro-wrestling days, I'm being overpowered...!? By
such a young girl...

Memimi: You say you've trained...? Your muscles, fattened by
squeezing taxes from the people without doing any real work,
are no match for my techniques, honed in actual combat!!

Shark Broccoli: Orca Asparagus... that's enough... You were
always a kind soul... Trying to buy that delicious powder,
you intended to give me the money so I could have it easy,
right?

Shark Broccoli: I'm returning this asparagus to you... I
kept it, dreaming of the day we could wrestle together
again... I'll join you, so let's atone for our sins and
start over...

Mayor Orca: Shark... my brother from the mountains... I...
but...!

Drillmaid: I'm begging you too, Orca Mountain!! Let's stop
this... Collecting money is just empty!! After all, the
times when you were there, and Shark Mountain's big brother
was there... those were the happiest...

Mayor Orca: Drillmaid... I... was I wrong...? No, maybe I've
always known... that I longed for this day to come...

Mayor Orca: I'm sorry... I've always been... just a kid...!
I couldn't bear it... that the three of us couldn't wrestle
together anymore...

Memimi: Haa haa... You're full of openings, Mayor Orca!! It
seems you're at your limit! I'll finish you off now!!!

Shark Broccoli: W-Wait a minute, Duke Shark... this is a
critical moment...

Bunny-chan: Victory goes to Duke Shark♪ With this, Mayor
Orca resigns from his position in Mudgain City! Introducing
the new mayor, Shark Broccoli-san!!!
Memimi has finally defeated Mayor Orca...!
